snippet.title: Undertale Red & Yellow 2.0 - Underevent 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
IT'S FINALLY HERE!!!!!!!!! It's been so, so difficult to keep my mouth shut, but the new update is OUT!
Check it out HERE! https://gamejolt.com/games/undertale-red-yellow/877387

It's been an honor to be a small part of Underevent, and it's been an honor to be able to make this update for you all!
